{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "梁斗被屈寒山骗走后，屈寒山命左常生将萧秋水带到七星岩五龙亭逼供杜月山剑谱。康劫生欲亲手杀萧秋水，此时长江四棍残余赶来寻仇。屈寒山留下应付四棍，命左常生等押萧秋水先行。在五龙亭，盛江北踢开萧秋水哑穴。萧秋水呼喊大肚和尚，其挚友了了大师从对面亭子渡水而来并解开其穴道。权力帮血影大师出手阻拦。随后广东五虎（刘友、吴财、罗海牛、阿杀、阿水）从天而降，为大肚和尚两肋插刀，与左常生、盛江北展开激战。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“你——！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“老盛，你这样，不怕‘家法’么？！”",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“差点给你累了大事！梁斗的武功，你又不是不知道，你连他都敢惹，你嫌命长是不是？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“帮主还要收拢他这等人物，是开罪不得的。为今之计，还是快做了这萧秋水，以免夜长梦多。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“只是杀了萧秋水，又如何向梁斗交代呢？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "text": "“我们杀了他后往大河一扔，谁知道他死了？日后要是听到他有什么消息，亦可说是我们放了他之后方才碰上的！没有真凭实据，梁斗也奈何不了我们！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“刚才我打你，其实是救你，要是梁斗真个要出手，你还有命在？！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“我们几人，加上您老，也不见得斗不过梁斗！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“多一事不如少一事，其实以屈剑王，武功自是在他之上，只不过还未到出手的时机罢了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "text": "“要杀梁斗，的确不难，但帮主未有明令，贸然行事，总是不妥。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“要杀萧秋水，倒不必劳诸位动手，他跟我有私仇，我来动手便是。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“萧秋水，你可怨不得我，是你不杀我的，我可要杀你了。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“慢着，要他把杜月山的剑谱逼供出来，再杀不迟！”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "常无奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是谁杀我老四？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是长江四棍？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“我们在这几人船上搜出萧秋水，当时他们其中一人在，背后还藏有尖刀，所以我们兄弟合力把他给杀了。”",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“反正朱老狐狸的手下都该杀。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“只是萧秋水怎会和朱老狐狸是一伙？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_dong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文栋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是谁暗杀我四弟的？！有种的站出来！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "text": "“这里我来应付，你们抓他先到七星岩的五龙亭去，我会到那儿找你们，记住要取得杜月山的剑谱。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“是！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_dong_lin",
      "speaker_name": "孟东林",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“想走！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“有我陪你们就够了。”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们就在这里等‘剑王’吧。听说待会儿‘血影’、‘狮公’、‘虎婆’也会来。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“快问出那剑谱的下落，好做了这小子！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“小子，聪明的快说出来，否则可以叫你后悔为何要生出来！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你不说，我先挑你双目！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不如先搜他身子，他一路上都被我们追赶，不可能有机会把剑谱收藏。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "text": "“这也有道理！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“大肚和尚！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“他妈的！他妈的！他妈的！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你这干八小子以后不准叫我大肚和尚。”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“那叫你鸟鸟大师好了。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你再叫，我揍你！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“好小子，你还想走！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying",
      "speaker_name": "血影大师",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“臭光头，要来撒野，先问过我血影大师！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“出来，出来！你们不出来，了了就要了帐了！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“喂，鸟鸟，你要我们救这人么？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you",
      "speaker_name": "刘友",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“喂，大肚，点子扎手得很呀。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_sha",
      "speaker_name": "阿杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这些人好像是权力帮的！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“权力帮的人不好惹啊！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不好惹么？我们广东五虎，专惹不好惹的人！”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“广东五只老虎仔，快跟我救此人，他是我死敌，也是我好友，更是我恩人，不救他，我们就连朋友都没得做，你们就是全广东最无用的五条老鼠仔！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you",
      "speaker_name": "刘友",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“广东老虎，岂是老鼠！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“给我好好瞧着，我们——打！”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不行，我们救人，总得要人知道我们的高姓大名。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you",
      "speaker_name": "刘友",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“正是。我叫刘友，潮阳人，人家叫我做‘疯女’。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我是揭阳吴财。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我系宝安罗海牛。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_sha",
      "speaker_name": "阿杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我珠江人，人家叫我阿杀，原名山仔。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我呢，我叫阿水，梅县阿水。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you",
      "speaker_name": "刘友",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们，就是广东五虎。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“永不分开的广东五虎。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“永不分开的广东五虎？我要把你们打成死蛇烂鳝！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“你这只无牙老鼠，我先来教训教训你！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_a_shui",
      "text": "“跛子也学人……！”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_a_shui",
      "text": "“看你这婆娘还凶不？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“不打了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“你这老王八，还不是喝了老娘的口水！”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“水姐歇歇，让我罗海牛来接这老乌龟两招！”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“这就是我自创的‘空手拳法’，你看怎样？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“不打了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“你武功好，我打不过你，你是气喘了，我胜了你也没意思。你还是休息休息吧。”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们呢，也别无所求，只要你们高抬贵手，不要为难这位朋友，我们就你走你的阳关道，我走我的独木桥……”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_wu_cai",
      "text": "“救人么？那可要问过我的双钹。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "text": "“问它么？破铜烂铁可不会应呀。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_wu_cai",
      "text": "“它说不可以！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "text": "“我这是风门舞姿，你打不着我的。”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_wu_cai",
      "text": "“小心——！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3
    }
  ],
